title: What is the price of a Google Pixel 5? - Quora

response.answer_text: New Google Pixel 5 is going to launch only in one variant named XL, and we will not get the low-budget variant of this smartphone. On the upcoming generation of Pixel phones, an online leaked report has said. As we saw on Twitter, this phone will be launched with a Qualcomm Snapdragon 765G processor, and it's priced located at $699 (roughly Rs. 52,200). This news arrives a few days back the Google Pixel 5 has spotted on a benchmark website with the mid-tier SoC.
